ISLAMABAD, Mar 28 (APP): Prime Minister Imran Khan would also join the housing telethon telephonically for a while today between 4:30 -6 p.m.
This was announced by senior leader of Pakistan Tehreek-e-Insaf Senator Shibli Faraz in a tweet on Sunday.
